# 🧠 Features

Welcome to **Text Speeder** — a lightweight, privacy-first speed-reading tool built to help users read faster, stay focused, and have full control over their reading experience.

---

## 🚀 Core Features

- ⚡ **Speed Reading Engine**  
  Instantly display text word by word at adjustable speeds to boost focus and reading efficiency.

- 🧭 **Simple, Minimal UI**  
  Clean and distraction-free interface optimized for both desktop and mobile.

- 🧠 **Custom Reading Speeds**  
  Fully adjustable WPM (Words Per Minute) to fit your comfort level.

- 🌓 **Dark / Light Theme**  
  Built-in theme toggle for comfortable reading day or night.

- 🪄 **Local Text Processing**  
  All text stays on your device. No account. No uploads. No tracking.

- 🔤 **Multiple Input Options**  
  Paste text directly or load local files to start reading instantly.

---

## 🧰 Additional Features

- ⌨️ **Keyboard Shortcuts** for faster control  
- 📱 **Mobile Responsive Design**  
- 🧼 No ads, popups, or unnecessary clutter  
- 🔒 Privacy-focused — nothing stored on our servers

---

## 🧪 Coming Soon (Roadmap Highlights)

- 🪁 Text-to-speech integration  
- 📝 Saved reading sessions  
- 📊 Personal reading analytics (local only)  
- 🌐 Optional multi-language support

👉 For more details on upcoming features, visit our [Roadmap](Roadmap).

